The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves transfer learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of unsupervised similarity measures also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of clustering, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging datasets, which could fall under the subcategory of multimedia (cs.MM).
